It would depend on which type of mirror, and thusly mirror arm  you are 
thinking of using!
 
Harp style
_http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/227704.jpg_ 
(http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/227704.jpg) 
 
Factory small round ones that any bus had from the factory on driver  side.  
Passenger side was optional.
_http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/206128.jpg_ 
(http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/206128.jpg) 
 
The one with the mirror head on, used same mirror heads as  arms above, but 
arm MUCH longer for wide bed single  cab truck.
